#: ../../guide/gui.rst:2
msgid "Graphical User Interface"
msgstr "Interface graphique"

#: ../../guide/gui.rst:4
msgid ""
"This package provides a simple graphical user interface to enable quick "
"calculations of x-ray transmission and absorption through materials. This "
"GUI makes use of `bokeh <https://bokeh.pydata.org>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ce paquet fournit une interface graphique simple pour permettre des calculs "
"rapides de transmission et d'absorption des rayons X à travers des "
"matériaux. Cette interface utilise `bokeh <https://bokeh.pydata.org>`_."

